**Week 7: Tokenized Sales**
- **Lecture Topics:**
  - Introduction to agri-marketplaces
  - How escrow protects both buyers and sellers
  - Fungible vs non-fungible token (NFT) crops
- **Exploration:**
  - Create SPL token for crop units (e.g., 1 token = 1 lb of potatoes)
  - Deploy escrow contract:

```rust
#[derive(Accounts)]
pub struct CreateSale<'info> {
    #[account(mut)]
    pub seller: Signer<'info>,
    #[account(init, payer = seller, space = 8 + Sale::LEN)]
    pub sale: Account<'info, Sale>,
    pub system_program: Program<'info, System>,
}

pub fn create_sale(ctx: Context<CreateSale>, price: u64, crop_type: u8) -> Result<()> {
    let sale = &mut ctx.accounts.sale;
    sale.price = price;
    sale.crop_type = crop_type;
    sale.is_active = true;
    Ok(())
}
